I used regular sourdough in a loaf and not the arisanal bread it calls for, all three nearby stores were out. So I used the crust from the loafs. I made this for a kosher meat meal and substituted pork sausage with chicken sausage and the butter with Earth's Balance. Very simple to make and tastes wonderful. Make sure your bowl is large enough to mix without spilling bits of bread over the rim.

